%% 帮扶管理信息系统 — Windows 离线安装包构建与运行时序图
%% 架构师：高见远

%% ===== 4.1 CI/CD 构建流程 =====
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Dev as 开发者
    participant GH as GitHub
    participant CI as CI Runner (win-2022)
    participant Node as Node.js 20
    participant Conda as Conda Python 3.11
    participant Vite as Vite Build
    participant PyI as PyInstaller
    participant EB as electron-builder
    participant NSIS as NSIS Compiler
    participant Rel as GitHub Release

    Dev->>GH: git push tag v1.2.0
    GH->>CI: trigger build-windows.yml (matrix: x64, x86)

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over CI,Conda: === 环境准备（每个 arch 并行）===
        CI->>Node: setup-node@v4 (Node 20)
        CI->>Conda: setup-miniconda@v3 (arch=x64 或 x86)
        Conda->>Conda: conda install numpy pandas scipy scikit-learn (预编译)
        CI->>CI: pip install -r requirements.txt + pyinstaller
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over CI,Vite: === 前端构建 ===
        CI->>Node: npm ci (frontend)
        Node->>Vite: npm run build
        Vite-->>CI: frontend/dist/ (index.html + assets)
        CI->>CI: cp frontend/dist → resources/frontend
    end

    rect rgb(248, 255, 240)
        Note over CI,PyI: === 后端打包 (PyInstaller) ===
        CI->>PyI: PyInstaller assistance-backend.spec --clean
        PyI->>PyI: Analysis(start.py) 收集依赖与数据文件
        PyI->>PyI: PYZ 压缩 Python 字节码
        PyI->>PyI: EXE 合并为单文件 (onefile, console=False)
        PyI-->>CI: backend/dist/assistance-backend.exe (~85MB)
        Note right of CI: 内含 Python 解释器 +<br/>全部 pip 依赖 + SQLite<br/>+ VC++ 运行时 DLL
    end

    rect rgb(248, 240, 255)
        Note over CI,NSIS: === Electron 打包 ===
        CI->>Node: npm ci (root, electron-builder)
        CI->>EB: electron-builder --win --x64 (或 --ia32)
        EB->>EB: 下载对应架构 Electron 二进制 (Chromium + Node.js)
        EB->>EB: 打包 electron/main.js + preload.js → app.asar
        EB->>EB: extraResources: backend/dist/assistance-backend.exe → resources/backend/
        EB->>EB: extraResources: frontend/dist → resources/frontend/
        EB->>EB: extraResources: resources/vcredist → resources/vcredist/
        EB->>EB: extraResources: resources/icon.png → resources/
        EB->>NSIS: 生成 NSIS 脚本 + 注入 electron-builder-nsis-hook.nsh
        NSIS->>NSIS: LZMA 压缩编译为 .exe
        NSIS-->>EB: 帮扶管理系统-Setup-1.2.0.exe
        EB-->>CI: dist/electron/帮扶管理系统-Setup-1.2.0.exe (~250MB)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 248)
        Note over CI,Rel: === 发布 ===
        CI->>GH: upload-artifact (windows-installer-x64 / windows-installer-x86)
        alt tag 触发 (refs/tags/v*)
            CI->>Rel: softprops/action-gh-release 创建 Release
            Rel->>Rel: 上传 x64 + x86 两个 .exe 安装包
            Rel-->>Dev: 发布完成通知
        end
    end


%% ===== 4.2 运行时启动流程 =====
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant User as 用户
    participant Exe as 安装包.exe
    participant NSIS as NSIS 安装器
    participant FS as 文件系统
    participant App as Electron App
    participant BE as assistance-backend.exe
    participant DB as SQLite (%LOCALAPPDATA%)

    Note over User,FS: === 安装阶段 ===
    User->>Exe: 双击运行安装包
    Exe->>NSIS: 启动安装向导
    NSIS->>NSIS: 检测架构 (x64/x86)
    NSIS->>FS: 静默安装 VC++ Redistributable (如缺失)
    NSIS->>FS: 解压到 C:\Program Files\帮扶管理系统\
    NSIS->>FS: 创建桌面快捷方式 + 开始菜单
    NSIS->>FS: 写入注册表卸载信息
    NSIS-->>User: 安装完成

    Note over User,DB: === 运行阶段 ===
    User->>App: 双击快捷方式启动
    App->>App: app.whenReady()
    App->>App: 显示 splash screen (加载动画)
    App->>App: findAvailablePort(8000, maxAttempts=11)
    App->>BE: spawn(assistance-backend.exe, env={DATABASE_URL, PORT, ...})

    rect rgb(240, 255, 248)
        Note over BE,DB: 后端初始化（PyInstaller 解压 + Python 启动）
        BE->>BE: 解压 _MEIPASS 到临时目录 (~2-3s)
        BE->>BE: 修复 stdout/stderr UTF-8 编码
        BE->>BE: apply_windows_proactor_fix() (WinError 10054)
        BE->>BE: ensure_runtime_secrets() 生成/加载密钥
        BE->>DB: 创建/打开 SQLite (首次自动建表迁移)
        BE->>BE: _verify_frontend_assets() 检查 resources/frontend
        BE->>BE: uvicorn.run(app, host=127.0.0.1, port)
        BE-->>App: GET /health 返回 200
    end

    App->>App: waitForBackend() 成功
    App->>App: 关闭 splash screen
    App->>App: createMainWindow()
    App->>BE: BrowserWindow.loadURL(http://127.0.0.1:{port})
    BE-->>App: 返回前端 HTML/JS/CSS (StaticFiles 服务)
    App->>User: 显示系统登录界面

    Note over App,BE: 用户使用：前端 ⇄ 后端 HTTP API 通信 (127.0.0.1)

    Note over User,App: === 退出阶段 ===
    User->>App: 点击关闭按钮
    App->>App: 隐藏窗口到系统托盘（非退出）
    User->>App: 托盘菜单 → 退出
    App->>App: isQuitting = true
    App->>BE: POST /api/v1/shutdown (X-Internal-Shutdown-Key)
    BE->>BE: uvicorn 优雅关闭 (完成进行中请求)
    App->>BE: taskkill /f /t (3s 超时兜底)
    App->>App: app.quit()
